reviews.text: Great environment to have a gathering with friends. Mexican food and beer are excellent. I use eatigo to reserve a table and there is an extra discount, therefore the price is cool.

Quality is consistent. Food is fresh and staffs are very accommodating.  They have self serve beer taps at each table, can be "dangerous" if you get too excited.

Please like if you find this helpful.

Excellent place, I am Mexican, even though is different from normal mexican cooking style I really enjoyed the food, it is delicious.  The place is cool and the service excellent. I really recommend this place
It was a good TexMex restaurant. The prices were pretty good for Hong Kong. We had the lunch special and it was tasty and more we could eat. I recommend it.
We had salad. For the prices I expected a lot better quality. The lettuce weren't fresh. Can't really recommend
